I'm coming too.

62
00:05:58,023 --> 00:06:00,346
I'm going for a walk.
Shine some light in the forest.

63
00:06:00,381 --> 00:06:02,394
If she's out there,
give her something to look at.

64
00:06:02,396 --> 00:06:05,441
- You think that's
a good idea right now?
- Dale.

65
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:18,307
( Moaning )

66
00:06:18,342 --> 00:06:21,387
Those windows,
what's on the other side?

67
00:06:21,421 --> 00:06:24,362
About a 20-foot drop
with nothing to catch you,
maybe some bushes,

68
00:06:24,389 --> 00:06:26,859
- then the athletic field.
- We just need enough time.

69
00:06:26,893 --> 00:06:29,061
We got to get up there.
We got to get 'em open
and get out.

70
00:06:29,097 --> 00:06:31,373
- Not me. Maybe you.
- Hey hey hey.

71
